{"tid":1790434,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發，可能係隱藏既絕招","createTime":"2019-12-20T03:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T12:29:20.000Z","uid":48044,"like":233,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"d2b37490ae5fde73a045d912d4723668c93ca1a1","tid":1790434,"uid":48044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:46:39.000Z","msg":"［何以這屎尿抺不走 ］和你「塞」攬炒版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1790293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1790293</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢個po之後忽發奇想<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，除左呢招之外，其實仲有一個方法可能被忽視左好耐，就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔小心將垃圾掉左落地下</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過其實正常人都唔鍾意污糟同臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以你唔會係垃圾站同污糟既公廁逗留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果我地係商場/黨鐵唔小心跌左垃圾落地下，咁會唔會變到令人唔想再去呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且，呢樣既成本好低，個個人都可以唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，既然個商場/黨鐵大家都唔妥，點解要對佢地盡公民責任保護佢地既環境清潔呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a966cae5c6e2f99f329d0cf516c3c837285f72","tid":1790434,"uid":48044,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"有冇人認同？"},{"pid":"7a6b5a3e5107fed59bdc4cde3d7bb7ba3694e1fa","tid":1790434,"uid":48044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2113249b4cc4a04abe1dfdeda20e5f37cb5200