e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2b37490ae5fde73a045d912d4723668c93ca1a1","tid":1790434,"uid":48044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:46:39.000Z","msg":"［何以這屎尿抺不走 ］和你「塞」攬炒版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1790293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1790293</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢個po之後忽發奇想<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，除左呢招之外，其實仲有一個方法可能被忽視左好耐，就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔小心將垃圾掉左落地下</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過其實正常人都唔鍾意污糟同臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以你唔會係垃圾站同污糟既公廁逗留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果我地係商場/黨鐵唔小心跌左垃圾落地下，咁會唔會變到令人唔想再去呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且，呢樣既成本好低，個個人都可以唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，既然個商場/黨鐵大家都唔妥，點解要對佢地盡公民責任保護佢地既環境清潔呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:39:49.000Z","msg":"將香港既商場搞到好似支那咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5009dbfd4bffa0a61b7d60eb3a2571725629d844","tid":1790434,"uid":240149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"借個位嚟推推 高質po 建立黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[突發]即時解決學生溫飽問題 請學生食飯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776541\" data-auto-link target=\"_bl